# comment-deeply-indented

## Input

```
        # deep comment
k v

```

## CST

```
SOURCE_FILE@0..27
  SPACE@0..8 "        "
  COMMENT@8..22
    SHARP@8..9 "#"
    SPACE@9..10 " "
    WORD@10..14 "deep"
    SPACE@14..15 " "
    WORD@15..22 "comment"
  NEWLINE@22..23 "\n"
  ENTRY@23..27
    WORD_KEY@23..24
      WORD@23..24 "k"
    SPACE@24..25 " "
    LINE_STRING@25..26
      STRING@25..26 "v"
    NEWLINE@26..27 "\n"
```

